OL,3,CWeekend weather: Could summer finally
OL,4,Cbe on its way?
OL,6,FEveryone has been talking about how
OL,7,Fchilly it's been this week!
OL,9,FThe northerly wind that has brought
OL,10,Fthat wintery feel will slowly start to
OL,11,Fmove on to a milder westerly over the
OL,12,Fweekend.
OL,14,FIt'll be cutting off that biting
OL,15,FArctic flow, before a warm southerly
OL,16,Fwind arrives through the middle of
OL,17,Fnext week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
