OL,3,CWeekend weather: Could summer finally
OL,4,Cbe on its way?
OL,6,FThat airflow, which is coming in off
OL,7,FEurope, is expected to boost
OL,8,Ftemperatures back into the 20's
OL,9,Fthroughout the second half of the week.
OL,11,FAnd with high pressure promising a
OL,12,Freturn next week too, things are
OL,13,Flooking promising as we head into the
OL,14,FBank Holiday.
OL,16,FFriday night
OL,18,FA few showers will drift southwards,
OL,19,Fbut many areas will be dry with clear
OL,20,Fspells.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
