OL,3,CWeekend weather: Could summer finally
OL,4,Cbe on its way?
OL,6,FCloud and rain are to arrive across
OL,7,Fthe far west towards dawn.
OL,9,FA patchy frost is possible in the
OL,10,Fcountryside, with temperatures in East
OL,11,FAnglia, as well as southern and
OL,12,Fwestern Scotland, expected to fall
OL,13,Fclose to freezing.
OL,15,FAn enhanced solar wind tonight will
OL,16,Fincrease the chance of being able to
OL,17,Fspot the Northern Lights across the
OL,18,Ftop of Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
