OL,3,CWeekend weather: Could summer finally
OL,4,Cbe on its way?
OL,6,FA sunny morning for most with an east
OL,7,F- west split developing across the UK.
OL,8,FCloud and rain are expected to
OL,9,Fgradually move into the west.
OL,11,FIt'll be staying dry and largely
OL,12,Fbright in the east for much of the
OL,13,Fday, but still chilly.
OL,15,FTemperatures will be reaching highs of
OL,16,F16C in London, but across the country
OL,17,Fmore widely it'll be 11 to 14C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
