OL,3,CWeekend weather: Could summer finally
OL,4,Cbe on its way?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAfter a milder night, Sunday is likely
OL,12,Fto be a day of sunshine and showers.
OL,14,FThese showers are likely to be
OL,15,Ffrequent and heavy across western
OL,16,FScotland and Northern Ireland and also
OL,17,Fsoutheast England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
