OL,3,CWeekend weather: Could summer finally
OL,4,Cbe on its way?
OL,6,FTemperatures are up a bit for
OL,7,Feveryone, with highs touching 17C in
OL,8,Fthe southeast, but more widely it is
OL,9,Fto be 13 to 16C.
